(WARBLE, ZAP!)

3
00:00:14,283 --> 00:00:16,843
(ROARS)

4
00:00:19,305 --> 00:00:20,436
♪ Adventure Time ♪

5
00:00:20,437 --> 00:00:21,802
♪ Come on, grab your friends ♪

6
00:00:21,803 --> 00:00:24,607
♪ We'll go to very messed-up lands ♪

7
00:00:24,608 --> 00:00:26,910
♪ With Finn and Jake,
Ice King, and Betty ♪

8
00:00:26,911 --> 00:00:28,482
♪ Who knows how it will end? ♪

9
00:00:28,483 --> 00:00:30,811
♪ It's Adventure Time ♪

10
00:00:32,318 --> 00:00:35,723
Sync and corrections by kay sukri

11
00:00:39,425 --> 00:00:41,493
(INDISTINCT CHANTING)

12
00:00:41,494 --> 00:00:43,494
FLAME CROWD: Smash the nerds!

13
00:00:43,495 --> 00:00:45,030
Smash the nerds!

14
00:00:45,031 --> 00:00:47,331
Nerds, nerds, smash the nerds!

15
00:00:47,332 --> 00:00:49,665
A nerdless world is the
best kind of world!

16
00:00:49,666 --> 00:00:51,969
Nerd, nerds, no more nerds!

17
00:00:51,970 --> 00:00:53,671
(GRUNTING) Heh... hah...

18
00:00:53,672 --> 00:00:55,473
Heh... hah...

19
00:00:55,474 --> 00:00:58,006
Heh... hah... hah...

20
00:00:58,007 --> 00:00:58,973
Finn!

21
00:00:58,974 --> 00:01:00,645
Fight, fight, fight.

22
00:01:00,646 --> 00:01:02,146
Finn, stop.

23
00:01:02,147 --> 00:01:04,618
What happened to getting the
fire jewel and saving Ooo?

24
00:01:04,619 --> 00:01:06,651
Is this about you ex?

25
00:01:06,652 --> 00:01:09,022
This is about the purity of battle.

26
00:01:09,672 --> 00:01:13,191
Okay, but you usually have
a reason for fighting.

27
00:01:13,192 --> 00:01:16,022
The fiery heartbeat of
battle is its own reason.

28
00:01:16,025 --> 00:01:18,028
No, that's stupid.

29
00:01:18,029 --> 00:01:19,461
- Yah!
- Oh, Glob!

30
00:01:19,462 --> 00:01:22,065
Just listen to the beat
of your hero heart.

31
00:01:22,066 --> 00:01:24,036
I only hear the drums of war.

32
00:01:24,078 --> 00:01:26,237
(GRUNTS)

33
00:01:26,238 --> 00:01:27,706
What drums?

34
00:01:27,707 --> 00:01:29,040
No!

35
00:01:29,041 --> 00:01:31,241
(GRUNTS) Finn!

36
00:01:31,242 --> 00:01:34,943
You're hurting me
physically and emotionally.

37
00:01:36,716 --> 00:01:38,347
(GRUNTS) Oh.

38
00:01:38,348 --> 00:01:39,713
Fight, fight...

39
00:01:39,714 --> 00:01:41,250
Dang it, Finn.

40
00:01:41,251 --> 00:01:43,753
Becoming a crazy, fiery bad boy

41
00:01:43,754 --> 00:01:45,696
has made you even more of a babe.

42
00:01:45,697 --> 00:01:47,754
ICE KING: Check it out, LSP.

43
00:01:47,755 --> 00:01:48,891
Wha?

44
00:01:48,892 --> 00:01:51,763
It's a real magic flying carpet.

45
00:01:51,764 --> 00:01:53,905
I feel just like Scheherazade.

46
00:01:53,907 --> 00:01:56,236
Lump creature, did you
get the fire jewel?

47
00:01:56,237 --> 00:01:59,204
No. Flame Princess freakin' ate it.

48
00:01:59,205 --> 00:02:01,675
And now the fire guys are
attacking the Candy Kingdom

49
00:02:01,676 --> 00:02:04,244
because they took everything
I said the wrong way.

50
00:02:04,245 --> 00:02:06,013
And that's totally on them.

51
00:02:06,014 --> 00:02:09,112
But also, we lost Finn
to the flames of war!

52
00:02:09,113 --> 00:02:10,746
Okay.

53
00:02:10,747 --> 00:02:13,413
I'll go find him.

54
00:02:13,414 --> 00:02:14,750
Finn?

55
00:02:14,751 --> 00:02:15,954
Finn?

56
00:02:15,955 --> 00:02:18,495
Oh, where are you, pal?

57
00:02:20,593 --> 00:02:22,260
(GASPS)

58
00:02:22,261 --> 00:02:23,392
It's Gunther.

59
00:02:23,393 --> 00:02:24,795
He's in flames, too.

60
00:02:24,796 --> 00:02:27,597
We have to rub soothing
lotion on Guntzy.

61
00:02:27,598 --> 00:02:28,963
You got any lotion?

62
00:02:28,964 --> 00:02:31,379
Your skin is so hydrated.

63
00:02:32,547 --> 00:02:33,802
FUN: Hmm.

64
00:02:34,815 --> 00:02:36,941
Got any...

65
00:02:36,942 --> 00:02:38,910
Caramel Crunch Pies?

66
00:02:38,911 --> 00:02:40,711
(GROANS)

67
00:02:40,712 --> 00:02:42,480
(LAUGHS) Yes!

68
00:02:42,481 --> 00:02:45,713
Oh, man, I don't think you should
play this game ever again.

69
00:02:45,714 --> 00:02:47,228
You're too good at it.

70
00:02:48,119 --> 00:02:49,783
What is that sound?

71
00:02:49,784 --> 00:02:54,153
(DRUMS BEATING IN DISTANCE)

72
00:02:54,154 --> 00:02:57,724
Ooh, company's coming!

73
00:02:57,725 --> 00:03:01,494
♪♪

74
00:03:01,495 --> 00:03:02,731
(BOTH CHEERING)

75
00:03:02,732 --> 00:03:04,002
Whoo!

76
00:03:04,003 --> 00:03:06,070
- Whoo!
- Yes!

77
00:03:06,071 --> 00:03:08,740
Mm! Look at all these thirsty customers!

78
00:03:08,741 --> 00:03:09,772
(DING!)

79
00:03:09,773 --> 00:03:12,310
Ooh, the pies are ready!

80
00:03:12,311 --> 00:03:16,311
Mm! Ice-cream pies for
all our hot new friends!

81
00:03:16,816 --> 00:03:18,483
Aah!

82
00:03:18,484 --> 00:03:22,320
(SIZZLING)

83
00:03:22,321 --> 00:03:25,353
(BOTH LAUGHING)

84
00:03:25,354 --> 00:03:26,991
Whoa! Mm!

85
00:03:26,992 --> 00:03:31,625
♪♪

86
00:03:31,626 --> 00:03:34,060
(SIZZLE!)

87
00:03:34,994 --> 00:03:36,964
Maybe they don't like lemonade.

88
00:03:36,966 --> 00:03:39,533
(LAUGHS)

89
00:03:39,535 --> 00:03:42,307
♪♪

90
00:03:42,308 --> 00:03:46,611
Gunther, your ride is here.

91
00:03:46,612 --> 00:03:48,072
(FOOSH!)

92
00:03:49,215 --> 00:03:52,015
Gee, who sneezed in your corn flakes?

93
00:03:52,016 --> 00:03:55,820
He's gone. The fire has taken his mind.

94
00:03:55,821 --> 00:03:57,690
Is this true, Goontz?

95
00:03:57,773 --> 00:04:00,191
Wenk! Wenk! Wenk!

96
00:04:00,192 --> 00:04:02,660
(FLAME CROWD GRUNTING)

97
00:04:02,661 --> 00:04:06,531
Look, weird lady, I don't know
you and you don't know me,

98
00:04:06,532 --> 00:04:08,532
but we're the only sane people left

99
00:04:08,533 --> 00:04:10,565
in this crazy, mixed-up world.

100
00:04:10,566 --> 00:04:12,000
Or maybe the world's fine

101
00:04:12,001 --> 00:04:14,236
and we're the ones losing our marbles.

102
00:04:14,237 --> 00:04:17,472
Either way, it's up to
us to save the day.

103
00:04:17,473 --> 00:04:18,543
Simon.

104
00:04:18,544 --> 00:04:22,245
So, let's get in there
and mash their potatoes.

105
00:04:22,246 --> 00:04:25,583
You got any mashed potatoes? I'm hungry.

106
00:04:25,584 --> 00:04:27,515
(BOTH SCREAM)

107
00:04:27,516 --> 00:04:28,982
Nerds.

108
00:04:28,983 --> 00:04:31,222
(PANTING)

109
00:04:31,223 --> 00:04:32,554
I have to hurry.

110
00:04:32,555 --> 00:04:34,898
All this chaos and
mayhem is just... ugh!

111
00:04:34,899 --> 00:04:36,894
Finn!

112
00:04:36,895 --> 00:04:39,163
You have to stop this.

113
00:04:39,164 --> 00:04:40,664
Think of Jake.

114
00:04:40,665 --> 00:04:43,735
How are you going to fix
him if you're a fire bozo?

115
00:04:43,736 --> 00:04:46,936
And if not for Jake, do it for me.

116
00:04:46,937 --> 00:04:49,239
Aah! Oh, my side.

117
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,404
FLAME CROWD: (CHANTING) Nerds,
nerds, smash the nerds!

118
00:04:51,405 --> 00:04:53,842
A nerdless world is the
best kind of world!

119
00:04:53,843 --> 00:04:55,916
- Nerd, nerds, no more nerds!
- (BUBBLEGUM HUMMING)

120
00:04:55,917 --> 00:04:59,115
My children have come home.

121
00:04:59,116 --> 00:05:01,218
We've come for<i> you!</i>

122
00:05:01,219 --> 00:05:04,252
Oh, a dragon, how fun!

123
00:05:04,253 --> 00:05:07,026
I can do a dragon. Look.

124
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,291
(ROARS)

125
00:05:09,292 --> 00:05:11,765
I see you've been playing with matches.

126
00:05:11,766 --> 00:05:13,464
Fight me, nerd!

127
00:05:14,433 --> 00:05:16,503
(GIGGLES)

128
00:05:17,436 --> 00:05:18,806
Whoo-hoo-hoo! (GIGGLES)

129
00:05:18,807 --> 00:05:22,674
Are we wrasslin'? Fun!

130
00:05:23,275 --> 00:05:26,811
- (GIGGLING)
- (GRUNTING)

131
00:05:26,812 --> 00:05:29,712
Aah! Stop having fun!

132
00:05:30,783 --> 00:05:32,783
Huh? (GASPS)

133
00:05:32,784 --> 00:05:34,752
Finn, no!

134
00:05:34,753 --> 00:05:35,953
Yah!

135
00:05:35,954 --> 00:05:37,455
This isn't you! (GRUNTS)

136
00:05:37,456 --> 00:05:40,591
You're being a very naughty boy, Finn!

137
00:05:40,592 --> 00:05:41,792
Oh, Glob.

138
00:05:41,793 --> 00:05:45,094
Everyone I know is spazzing
out on each other.

139
00:05:45,095 --> 00:05:47,137
They're spazzing each other to death!

140
00:05:47,138 --> 00:05:48,632
(FOOSH!)

141
00:05:50,636 --> 00:05:52,136
(FOOSH!)

142
00:05:52,137 --> 00:05:55,173
Is this the end?

143
00:05:55,174 --> 00:05:56,805
Will I be the last witness

144
00:05:56,806 --> 00:06:00,309
to the glory of this world
that I chose above all others?

145
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:03,312
(MARSHMALINE GIGGLING)

146
00:06:03,313 --> 00:06:05,515
Tickle, tickle, tickle. (GIGGLES)

147
00:06:08,954 --> 00:06:10,021
(GASPS)

148
00:06:10,022 --> 00:06:13,791
Marceline! I got you!

149
00:06:13,792 --> 00:06:15,924
(SPLAT!)

150
00:06:15,925 --> 00:06:17,261
(GROANS)

151
00:06:17,262 --> 00:06:19,030
I got<i> burned.</i>

152
00:06:19,031 --> 00:06:20,462
(LAUGHS WEAKLY)

153
00:06:20,463 --> 00:06:22,500
Oh, Marcy.

154
00:06:22,501 --> 00:06:25,264
I don't think I can save
the world on my own.

155
00:06:25,265 --> 00:06:27,770
I'm more of an aspiring
hero than a real one.

156
00:06:27,771 --> 00:06:32,043
I got, like, the morals and the
charisma and the good looks,

157
00:06:32,044 --> 00:06:35,513
but I lack field experience!

158
00:06:35,514 --> 00:06:39,384
Why couldn't I just get
morphed like everyone else?

159
00:06:39,385 --> 00:06:42,385
Curse these superior genes!

160
00:06:43,155 --> 00:06:44,186
(LAUGHS)

161
00:06:44,187 --> 00:06:46,189
Have some marshmallow, dude.

162
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:48,354
It'll calm you down.

163
00:06:48,355 --> 00:06:49,860
Mm.

164
00:06:51,463 --> 00:06:53,631
(SLURPS) Mmm.

165
00:06:53,632 --> 00:06:55,532
(MUNCHES)

166
00:06:55,533 --> 00:07:00,134
(INHALES, EXHALES DEEPLY)

167
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:05,510
(SOFTLY) Your face tastes
like my happy place.

168
00:07:05,511 --> 00:07:06,842
FIRE FINN: Rah! (SWORD SWINGS)

169
00:07:06,843 --> 00:07:08,176
(GASPS)

170
00:07:08,177 --> 00:07:09,211
Ahh!

171
00:07:09,212 --> 00:07:10,381
Fire Finn rules!

172
00:07:10,382 --> 00:07:14,314
(GRUNTING) Hah... hah... hah.

173
00:07:14,315 --> 00:07:16,719
It's time to go professional.

174
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:19,422
Hah... hah... yah.

175
00:07:19,423 --> 00:07:20,756
Finn!

176
00:07:20,757 --> 00:07:22,422
My little sugarplum.

177
00:07:22,423 --> 00:07:25,563
You've returned to
accept your sweet fate.

178
00:07:25,564 --> 00:07:27,231
I ain't sweet!

179
00:07:27,232 --> 00:07:29,232
I'm a pure warrior with guns,

180
00:07:29,233 --> 00:07:32,003
and I'ma murder you for funs!

181
00:07:32,004 --> 00:07:33,904
Rahhh!

182
00:07:33,905 --> 00:07:35,573
No!

183
00:07:35,574 --> 00:07:38,874
You can't stab a person you love, Finn!

184
00:07:38,875 --> 00:07:40,777
I'll stab you!

185
00:07:40,778 --> 00:07:42,339
- Aah!
- Oof!

186
00:07:43,882 --> 00:07:45,550
Hmm.

187
00:07:45,551 --> 00:07:48,114
I'm sending you to your...

188
00:07:48,115 --> 00:07:49,783
happy place!

189
00:07:49,784 --> 00:07:50,855
(SIZZLE!)

190
00:07:50,856 --> 00:07:53,224
(SNIFFS, SNORTS)

191
00:07:53,225 --> 00:07:57,325
♪♪

192
00:07:58,063 --> 00:08:00,663
Here, take it, you cutie.

193
00:08:02,568 --> 00:08:03,601
Rawr!

194
00:08:03,602 --> 00:08:06,602
LSP: (ECHOING) I said your happy place.

195
00:08:06,603 --> 00:08:10,106
Happy place!

196
00:08:10,107 --> 00:08:13,609
I wish I could stay like this.

197
00:08:13,610 --> 00:08:14,743
(FOOSH!)

198
00:08:14,744 --> 00:08:16,280
(SIZZLE!)

199
00:08:16,281 --> 00:08:18,644
I've enjoyed just... just hanging out.

200
00:08:18,645 --> 00:08:19,910
Me too.

201
00:08:27,126 --> 00:08:30,661
(SOFT SIZZLING)

202
00:08:30,662 --> 00:08:32,162
You did it, LSP.

203
00:08:32,163 --> 00:08:33,574
I'm human Finn.

204
00:08:35,117 --> 00:08:37,001
There's no time for romance, Finn.

205
00:08:37,002 --> 00:08:39,270
We got to get that jewel.

206
00:08:39,271 --> 00:08:40,634
Oh, yeah.

207
00:08:40,635 --> 00:08:42,002
Hup!

208
00:08:42,003 --> 00:08:44,307
I'm bringing you back, Bonnie.

209
00:08:44,308 --> 00:08:46,141
(GIGGLES)

210
00:08:46,142 --> 00:08:47,812
That's sweet.

211
00:08:47,813 --> 00:08:49,080
Hup.

212
00:08:49,081 --> 00:08:50,312
Aah!

213
00:08:50,313 --> 00:08:54,485
Sweet, but not sweet enough.

214
00:08:54,486 --> 00:08:56,821
(BOTH SCREAMING) (GIGGLING)

215
00:08:56,822 --> 00:08:58,252
Eeh!

216
00:08:58,924 --> 00:08:59,991
Ugh!

217
00:08:59,992 --> 00:09:04,825
(RUMBLING, BUBBLEGUM GRUNTING)

218
00:09:04,826 --> 00:09:07,693
This charade has run its course.

219
00:09:07,694 --> 00:09:12,269
In your hearts, you are all sweet.

220
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:17,172
♪ Let me call you sweetheart ♪

221
00:09:17,173 --> 00:09:21,512
♪ I'm in love with you ♪

222
00:09:21,513 --> 00:09:22,680
Wenk.

223
00:09:22,681 --> 00:09:25,781
♪ Let me hear you whisper ♪ (GASPING)

224
00:09:25,782 --> 00:09:27,284
Let my impervious bod be your shield!

225
00:09:27,285 --> 00:09:29,720
♪ That you love me, too ♪ Mmm!

226
00:09:29,721 --> 00:09:31,953
(SCREAMS)

227
00:09:31,954 --> 00:09:35,157
♪ Keep the love-light glowing ♪ No!

228
00:09:35,158 --> 00:09:36,291
(GASPS) Flame Princess!

229
00:09:36,292 --> 00:09:38,995
♪ In your eyes so true ♪

230
00:09:38,996 --> 00:09:41,197
(COUGHS) Phoebe?

231
00:09:41,198 --> 00:09:43,831
♪ Let me call you sweetheart
♪ (CANDY RATTLING)

232
00:09:43,832 --> 00:09:45,035
(GAGS)

233
00:09:45,036 --> 00:09:49,340
♪ I'm in love with you ♪

234
00:09:49,341 --> 00:09:50,372
The final jujubee.

235
00:09:50,373 --> 00:09:51,945
BETTY: Finn!

236
00:09:53,645 --> 00:09:56,145
Mm-hmm.

237
00:09:56,146 --> 00:09:57,215
Hmm.

238
00:09:57,216 --> 00:09:59,716
(GOBBLING)

239
00:09:59,717 --> 00:10:03,654
Purple clump, you are a sour anomaly.

240
00:10:03,655 --> 00:10:04,655
Whuh?

241
00:10:04,656 --> 00:10:06,096
(MUFFLED) What'd you call me?

242
00:10:06,097 --> 00:10:09,391
(CANDY RATTLING) Aah!

243
00:10:09,392 --> 00:10:12,563
Give me them jewels,
Finn. We're out of time.

244
00:10:12,564 --> 00:10:13,934
Give me, give me, give me.

245
00:10:13,935 --> 00:10:15,095
Here.

246
00:10:15,096 --> 00:10:16,731
(CACKLES)

247
00:10:16,732 --> 00:10:20,075
Now, let's grab LSP and get
the buns out of here...

248
00:10:20,076 --> 00:10:21,703
Hoh.

249
00:10:21,704 --> 00:10:23,074
Huh?

250
00:10:23,075 --> 00:10:29,345
(CACKLING)

251
00:10:29,346 --> 00:10:30,818
(TING!)

252
00:10:31,617 --> 00:10:33,584
I've been betrayed.

253
00:10:33,585 --> 00:10:35,785
I've been Betty-trayed!

254
00:10:35,786 --> 00:10:37,657
(RUSTLING)

255
00:10:38,857 --> 00:10:40,391
(SCREAMS)

256
00:10:40,392 --> 00:10:43,924
♪ Let me call you sweetheart ♪

257
00:10:43,925 --> 00:10:48,130
ALL: ♪ I'm in love with you ♪

258
